title: SMART Bus Stops
description: Suburban Mobility Authority for Regional Transportation (SMART) bus stops. Data originally sourced from Data Driven Detroit.

title: Current Master Plan Future General Land Use
description: The following field definitions make up the shapefile attribute table called Master Plan of Policies Future General Land Use Map for City of Detroit adopted in 2009. This shapefile consists of all areas in the city defined with the Master Plan of Policies Future General Land Use Map. The Master Plan Future General Land Use Map has been amended since it was adopted. The layer was amended on October 17, 2017.
